data.description: Country City living at its Finest!!!! 5.96 Acres conveniently located in the heart of Alvin with 2.5 acres that run on the side and 3 in the back. This property comes with a 5BD/3BA Manufactured home and 2BD/1BA Garage Apt with 506' frontage on South Durant Street within walking distance to Alvin High School. Both structures are in average condition and great for reconstruction. This lot lies in Brazoria County and can be used for residential or multi-use. Three sheds will stay along with a 48x36 cement pad installed with power that runs to it. Easy access to Highway 6 and Alvin Bypass. Near Alvin schools and 30 Miles to George Bush Intercontinental Airport . This property has endless possibilities for redevelopment.  All utilities on site!!! This one won't last long!!!!
